        <%= image_tag 'earthskipper-1.png', class: "visible content" %>
        <%= image_tag 'earthskipper-2.png', class: "hidden content" %>
      </div>
      <div class="content">
        <div class="header center aligned">EarthSkipper</div>
        <div class="meta center aligned">
          <a>Hackathon Project</a>
        </div>
        <div class="description">
          Written, tested, and deployed in under 24 hours. EarthSkipper is a web-application to promote spontaneous travel around the world. Developed using <strong>Ruby on Rails</strong>, <strong>FourSquare API</strong>, and <strong>Amazon S3</strong>. Awarded 'Best First Hack' at the University of Miami's hackathon <strong>UHack 2018</strong>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="extra content">
        <span class="right floated">
          Developed in 2018
        </span>
        <span>
          <a href="https://github.com/pablof300/EarthSkipper">
            <i class="linkify icon"></i>
            View more
          </a>
        </span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="blue card" id="third-project" data-content="This project made me realize I love tinkering with electronics and the programming behind physical actuators!" data-title="Fun fact" data-position="top center">
