          Interactive RFID-capable hydraulic powered orangutan that raises awareness about his specie/environment through speech. I was the lead engineer for wiring and programming, using a <strong>Raspberry PI</strong> and <strong>Python</strong>. Second place winner at the 2018 Technology Student Association Florida State conference.
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="extra content">
        <span class="right floated">
          Developed in 2018
        </span>
        <span>
